{"data":[{"date":"07:10 19/08","title":"Lionel Messi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 6000 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed La Liga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/lionel-messi-lap-cot-moc-6000-tai-la-liga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Ernesto Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Philippe Coutinho - nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \"ba sao\" c\u1ee7a Barcelona tr\u01b0\u1edbc Alaves.</h2><h2>B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Messi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Alaves l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Lionel Messi ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia. V\u00e0 ch\u00ednh &quot;Leo&quot; l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn hai pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn khung g\u1ed7 gi\u00fap Barca gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde nhan xet bat ngo ve Lionel Messi sau tran thang Alaves.\" title=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Alaves.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/hlv-ernesto-valverde-nhan-xet-bat-ngo-ve-lionel-messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Ernesto Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Alaves.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Ernesto Valverde th\u1ed1t l\u00ean: &quot;Messi lu\u00f4n khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. Anh \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i ng\u1eebng kinh ng\u1ea1c. Th\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea5y&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 6.000 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed La Liga. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap Barca chia s\u1ebb ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Levante khi b\u1eb1ng v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Valverde gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Valverde ch\u01b0a s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t khi c\u00f2n c\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf ngo\u00e0i nh\u01b0 Coutinho. Nh\u00f3m t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t, Arthur v\u00e0 Vidal ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, HLV Valverde cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tr\u00e1nh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng hi\u1ec7p hai l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 Coutinho v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i b\u00f3ng, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec c\u1ea3. S\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00ean m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng&quot;.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Barca m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/lich-thi-dau/lionel-messi-lap-cot-moc-6000-tai-la-liga-181-194781.html\">Lionel Messi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 6000 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed La Liga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-barca-vs-alaves-30-highlights-la-liga-2018-328-194780.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Barca 3-0 Alaves (V\u00f2ng 1 La Liga 2018/19)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/barca-vs-alaves-la-liga-1882018-372-194762.html\">Barca 3-0 Alaves: Messi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, Blaugrana ra qu\u00e2n nh\u01b0 \u00fd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tan-binh-tai-tieng-cua-barca-hanh-phuc-sau-man-chao-san-camp-nou-180-194707.html\">T\u00e2n binh tai ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Barca h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n Camp Nou</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/anh-trai-messi-di-tu-vi-toi-tang-tru-vu-khi-188-194681.html\">Anh trai Messi \u0111i t\u00f9 v\u00ec t\u1ed9i t\u00e0ng tr\u1eef v\u0169 kh\u00ed</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/lionel-messi-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-cua-barca-mua-toi-180-194656.html\">Lionel Messi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1ed1i th\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Barca m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2525","checkdouble":"194781"},{"date":"07:17 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield (19h30 ng\u00e0y 19/8): \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-man-city-vs-huddersfield-19h30-ngay-198-don-gian-la-chua-the-can.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u00eam ba \u0111i\u1ec3m thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c n\u1eefa ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau duy nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n trong t\u1ea7m tay c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u00ec m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n Etihad ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o nh\u1ea5t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u l\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng Premier League, Manchester City kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi v\u1eabn nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc v\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd ch\u1eb3ng tr\u1ea3i qua ba th\u00e1ng ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 n\u00e0o h\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield 19h30 ng\u00e0y 198 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield 19h30 ng\u00e0y 198 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-man-city-vs-huddersfield-19h30-ngay-198-don-gian-la-chua-the-can.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, hai b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng ph\u01a1i x\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u00e2n th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i d\u1ea1ng v\u1eeba ch\u00fat n\u00e0o, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal. Ch\u1eb3ng quan tr\u1ecdng, nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u1edf Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh r\u1ed3i ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">S\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a Man City c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 n\u00e9t \u1edf vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t hay s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Etihad \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Kh\u00f4ng Nicolas Otamendi, David Silva hay c\u1ea3 Kevin De Bruyne, n\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester v\u1eabn b\u0103ng b\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-arsenal-02-man-city-sterling-va-cau-tra-loi-cho-ca-nuoc-anh-172-194405.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/du-am-arsenal-02-man-city-sterling-va-cau-tra-loi-cho-ca-nuoc-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-arsenal-02-man-city-sterling-va-cau-tra-loi-cho-ca-nuoc-anh-172-194405.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Arsenal 0-2 Man City: Sterling v\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Raheem Sterling m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Man City trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ebf n\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn ba th\u00e1ng xem ra kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eb7n g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Man City, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u00eanh thang v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu, cho \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng M\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea1i mang t\u00ean Liverpool.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng De Bruyne, Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i qu\u1ef5 ng\u00e3, th\u1ebf n\u00ean nh\u1eefng Huddersfield hay Wolverhampton, Newcastle, Fulham, Cardiff, Brighton s\u1eafp t\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec khi ngh\u00eanh chi\u1ebfn nh\u00e0 vua, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t Bernardo Silva nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp thay th\u1ebf De Bruyne, hay t\u00e2n binh bom t\u1ea5n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c Riyad Mahrez, c\u1ea3 Benjamin Mendy v\u00e0 Aymeric Laporte c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c n\u00e0o nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi khi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling tran Arsenal vs Man City\" title=\"Sterling tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/Du-am-Arsenal-0-2-Man-City-Sterling-va-cau-tra-loi-cho-ca-nuoc-Anh-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Etihad c\u1ee7a Huddersfield Town c\u00f3 ch\u0103ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u00e0ng \u00edt b\u00e0n thua c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng th\u00e0nh Manchester c\u0169ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">S\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh gi\u1eadm ch\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ch\u1ed7, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i th\u1ee5t l\u00f9i, trong khi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u0169ng d\u1ea7n b\u1ecb b\u1eaft b\u00e0i v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3, Huddersfield ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn bu\u00f4ng xu\u00f4i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 Chelsea h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t ba b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu t\u00ednh chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 David Wagner.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thong-diep-tu-huddersfield-hay-cu-tin-di-va-dung-bao-gio-ngung-172-185994.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/10/DcyGxr0W4AA33Sj.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thong-diep-tu-huddersfield-hay-cu-tin-di-va-dung-bao-gio-ngung-172-185994.html\">Th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p t\u1eeb Huddersfield: H\u00e3y c\u1ee9 tin \u0111i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eebng bao ng\u1edd ng\u1eebng!</span><br>\r\nC\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Chelsea ngay tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t kh\u00e1ch Stamford Bridge, Huddersfield tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng Premier League th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 vi\u1ebft n\u00ean c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5 t\u00edch gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1eddi th\u1ef1c cho ri\u00eang...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ef1a trung l\u1ea1i, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 Man City c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 t\u1ed1i nay, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1eb7t ra l\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd th\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t bao nhi\u00eau m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng c\u0169ng v\u1edbi chuy\u1ebfn vi\u1ebfng th\u0103m Etihad g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t, ch\u00ednh Huddersfield \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ng\u00e0y vui s\u1edbm \u0111\u0103ng quang v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1eady n\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola r\u00fat ra kinh nghi\u1ec7m. N\u1ebfu ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 th\u00ec r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, Huddersfield kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ch\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u1ea1i v\u1eadt \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n b\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 vua ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield 19h30 ng\u00e0y 198 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield 19h30 ng\u00e0y 198 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/Nhan-dinh-Man-City-vs-Huddersfield-19h30-ngay-198-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Man City (4-3-3): 31. Ederson; 2. Walker \u2013 5. Stones \u2013 14. Laporte \u2013 22. Mendy; 8. Gundogan \u2013 25. Fernandinho \u2013 20. Bernardo; 26. Mahrez \u2013 33. Jesus \u2013 7. Sterling<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Huddersfield (4-2-3-1): 12. Hamer; 33. Hadergjonaj \u2013 26. Schindler \u2013 5. Kongolo \u2013 15. Lowe; 10. Mooy \u2013 6. Hogg; 17. Van La Parra \u2013 21. Pritchard \u2013 11. Diakhaby; 24. Mounie<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City vs Huddersfield: 4-0<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p><strong><br>\r\n</strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2524","checkdouble":"194783"},{"date":"07:25 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (16h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8): Khi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nhat-ban-16h00-ngay-198-khi-3-diem-khong-con-nhieu-y-nghia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay 19/8, c\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn tranh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u r\u1eb1ng HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hay gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7?\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; khi gi\u1eef l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 sau hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u khi c\u00f3 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/ b\u1ea1i l\u00e0 +5 (b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt song t\u1ea1m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u BXH b\u1ea3ng D do h\u01a1n hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 fair-play. N\u1ebfu \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, hai \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u00f2a nhau th\u00ec sau 90 ph\u00fat, Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (16h00 ng\u00e0y 198) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (16h00 ng\u00e0y 198) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/Nhan-dinh-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Nhat-Ban-(16h00-ngay-198)-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ea7y Park c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u1ee7a 1 trong 3 b\u1ea3ng B/E/F, trong khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D g\u1eb7p nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng E. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a, d\u00f9 th\u1eafng, h\u00f2a hay b\u1ea1i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i th\u00ec \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo 99% kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e1p m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kim chi \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0nh cho 16 \u0111\u1ed9i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 v\u1edbi b\u1ed1 c\u1ea3nh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng thua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd n\u1eb1m c\u00f9ng nh\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Uzbekistan, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh 1 su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft th\u00ec nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1nh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd t\u00ednh to\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng &ldquo;bu\u00f4ng&rdquo; tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 m\u1ed1i lo ng\u1ea1i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n, kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Khi \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u1edf cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn chi\u1ec1u nay nh\u1eb1m c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bang D ASIAD\" title=\"B\u1ea3ng D ASIAD\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Bang-D-ASIAD.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D l\u00fac n\u00e0y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm vinh quang t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 v\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea3o. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. V\u00e0 v\u00ec th\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n &ndash; khi danh hi\u1ec7u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 mang \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb U21 tham d\u1ef1 nh\u1eb1m c\u1ecd s\u00e1t v\u00e0 trau d\u1ed3i kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi Olympic Tokyo 2020, k\u1ef3 th\u1ebf v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i m\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng b\u1edfi l\u00fd do \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng toan t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan, Nepal \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Vi\u1ec7t Nam. D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 mang \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0ng Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, nh\u1edd s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Pakistan vs U23 Nhat Ban\" title=\"U23 Pakistan vs U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/u23-nhat-ban-vs-u23-pakistan-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ebb c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m t\u1eebng \u0111\u0103ng quang gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Saudi Arabia l\u00e0 Thebault Yamaguchi v\u00e0 Tatsuya Ito. V\u00e0 d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i U21, song ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u0169ng c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Uzbekistan, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed9i U21 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u00f9 c\u00f3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t. T\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn nay, Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1eeb c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ebb cho \u0111\u1ebfn \u0110TQG. Tr\u1ea3i qua 4 l\u1ea7n so t\u00e0i cao th\u1ea5p, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf to\u00e0n thua, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng mang t\u00ednh danh d\u1ef1.&nbsp;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u1edbi s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i b\u00e0n tay c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sau l\u00fac n\u00e0y 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 n\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd bu\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh cho v\u00f2ng 1/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn, t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u nay. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a 2 \u0111\u1ed9i:</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng; Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, Duy M\u1ea1nh, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, V\u0103n L\u1ee3i, V\u0103n Thanh; \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Ryosuke Kojima; Takahiro Yanagi; Teruki Hara; Honoya Shoji; Taiyo Koga; So Fujitani; Itsuki Urata; Koji Miyoshi; Tsukasa Morishima; Kyosuke Tagawa; Ren Komatsu.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: 0-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2523","checkdouble":"194784"},{"date":"07:48 19/08","title":"HLV Ernesto Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/hlv-ernesto-valverde-nhan-xet-bat-ngo-ve-lionel-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Ernesto Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Philippe Coutinho - nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \"ba sao\" c\u1ee7a Barcelona tr\u01b0\u1edbc Alaves.</h2><h2>B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Messi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Alaves l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Lionel Messi ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia. V\u00e0 ch\u00ednh &quot;Leo&quot; l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn hai pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn khung g\u1ed7 gi\u00fap Barca gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde nhan xet bat ngo ve Lionel Messi sau tran thang Alaves.\" title=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Alaves.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/hlv-ernesto-valverde-nhan-xet-bat-ngo-ve-lionel-messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Ernesto Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Alaves.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Ernesto Valverde th\u1ed1t l\u00ean: &quot;Messi lu\u00f4n khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. Anh \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i ng\u1eebng kinh ng\u1ea1c. Th\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea5y&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 6.000 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed La Liga. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap Barca chia s\u1ebb ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Levante khi b\u1eb1ng v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Valverde gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Valverde ch\u01b0a s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t khi c\u00f2n c\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf ngo\u00e0i nh\u01b0 Coutinho. Nh\u00f3m t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t, Arthur v\u00e0 Vidal ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, HLV Valverde cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tr\u00e1nh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng hi\u1ec7p hai l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 Coutinho v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i b\u00f3ng, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec c\u1ea3. S\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00ean m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng&quot;.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Barca m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/lich-thi-dau/lionel-messi-lap-cot-moc-6000-tai-la-liga-181-194781.html\">Lionel Messi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 6000 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed La Liga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-barca-vs-alaves-30-highlights-la-liga-2018-328-194780.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Barca 3-0 Alaves (V\u00f2ng 1 La Liga 2018/19)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/barca-vs-alaves-la-liga-1882018-372-194762.html\">Barca 3-0 Alaves: Messi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, Blaugrana ra qu\u00e2n nh\u01b0 \u00fd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tan-binh-tai-tieng-cua-barca-hanh-phuc-sau-man-chao-san-camp-nou-180-194707.html\">T\u00e2n binh tai ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Barca h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n Camp Nou</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/anh-trai-messi-di-tu-vi-toi-tang-tru-vu-khi-188-194681.html\">Anh trai Messi \u0111i t\u00f9 v\u00ec t\u1ed9i t\u00e0ng tr\u1eef v\u0169 kh\u00ed</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlere