ton-vs-man-utd-22h00-ngay-198-cau-tra-loi-tren-san-co.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 Old Trafford \u0111ang r\u1ed1i ren v\u00ec \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf Premier League s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n th\u1ea5t thi\u1ec7t.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Manchester United b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00e1 t\u1ec7 t\u1eeb chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ebft b\u00e1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch, m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m v\u00e0 r\u1ed1i ren \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 xoay quanh Jose Mourinho v\u1edbi m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn t\u1eeb ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t Paul Pogba.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Brighton vs Man Utd\" title=\"Preview Brighton vs Man Utd\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/Preview-Brighton-vs-Man-Utd.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs MU v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">R\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 \u00f4ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb d\u00f9 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester City gi\u00fap Man Utd tr\u00fat b\u1ecf r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eefng tin h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, v\u00e0 n\u00f3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd ngay sau \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1eafm b\u1eaft tinh th\u1ea7n hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a MU khi m\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, h\u1ecd cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi phong \u0111\u1ed9, khi Pogba v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111eo tay ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf World Cup 2018, trong khi Luke Shaw c\u0169ng \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-20-leicester-172-194221.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/du-am-mu-20-leicester.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-20-leicester-172-194221.html\">Man Utd m\u1edf m\u00e0n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb: Kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung v\u1ec7? Kh\u00f4ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1!</span><br>\r\nPaul Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1, Luke Shaw h\u1ed3i sinh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh c\u1eb7p b\u00e0i tr\u00f9ng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Eric Bailly v\u00e0 Victor Lindelof \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng MU 2-1 Leicester...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00ednh Pogba l\u1ea1i ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p h\u00f3a m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 l\u00ean v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u1ee1m \u1edd kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Mourinho c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111i \u1edf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Falmer, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi ra ti\u1ebfng v\u00e0o v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1eabn \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u00f9 sao v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 binh h\u00f9ng t\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1ea1nh, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Romelu Lukaku tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1ed1i th\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Man Utd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 v\u1edbi ba \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n r\u1eddi mi\u1ec1n bi\u1ec3n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nam, n\u01a1i h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua c\u1ea3 ba t\u00e2n binh Premier League trong c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs Man Utd (22h00 ng\u00e0y 198) C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs Man Utd (22h00 ng\u00e0y 198) C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Nhan-dinh-Brighton-vs-Man-Utd-(22h00-ngay-198)-Cau-tra-loi-tren-san-co-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs MU v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ni\u1ec1m tin c\u0169ng c\u00e0ng v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng h\u01a1n khi tr\u00f4ng sang t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn. Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, Brighton g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 thay m\u00e1u to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh khi chia tay \u0111\u1ebfn 28 c\u00e1i t\u00ean, t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t g\u1eafn b\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng \u00edt tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n sau khi h\u1ebft th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho 16 t\u00e2n binh khao kh\u00e1t th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 t\u00e1o b\u1ea1o \u0111\u00f3 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Watford trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n Premier League 2018/19 n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ebft b\u00e1t t\u1eeb h\u00e8 v\u1edbi v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t qua s\u00e1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Brighton ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 th\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Cho n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ba \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf l\u1ea1i Falmer trong m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch MU t\u1ed1i nay c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i l\u1eadp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs Man Utd (22h00 ng\u00e0y 198) C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs Man Utd (22h00 ng\u00e0y 198) C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/Nhan-dinh-Brighton-vs-Man-Utd-(22h00-ngay-198)-Cau-tra-loi-tren-san-co-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs MU v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs MU:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Brighton (4-4-1-1): 1. Ryan; 22. Montoya \u2013 4. Duffy \u2013 5. Dunk \u2013 30. Bernardo; 16. Jahanbakhsh \u2013 6. Stephens \u2013 8. Bissouma \u2013 20. March; 13. Gross \u2013 17. Murray<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Man Utd (4-3-3): 1. De Gea; 18. Young \u2013 3. Bailly \u2013 2. Lindelof \u2013 23. Shaw; 17. Fred \u2013 15. Pereira \u2013 6. Pogba; 8. Mata \u2013 9. Lukaku \u2013 7. Sanchez<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brighton vs MU: 1-2<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p><strong><br>\r\n</strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2520","checkdouble":"194787"},{"date":"08:31 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Getafe (3h15 ng\u00e0y 20/8): Barca g\u1ecdi, Real s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-getafe-3h15-ngay-208-barca-goi-real-se-tra-loi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Barca \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Alaves, CLB Real Madrid c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 th\u1eadt may \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Getafe kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN m\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u cho m\u1ed9t tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Bernabeu &ndash; tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Julen Lopetegui.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay. Th\u1eadt may, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Barcelona, th\u1eed th\u00e1ch d\u00e0nh cho Real Madrid trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, khi h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea7m trung Getafe.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Getafe (3h15 ng\u00e0y 208) Barca g\u1ecdi, Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Getafe (3h15 ng\u00e0y 208) Barca g\u1ecdi, Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/Nhan-dinh-Real-Madrid-vs-Getafe-(3h15-ngay-208)-Barca-goi,-Real-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Lopetegui \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi gi\u1eefa Real Madrid vs Getafe</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 n\u1eb1m c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 v\u1edbi Real nh\u01b0ng CLB Getafe ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 so b\u00ec v\u1edbi Los Blancos \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0o, t\u1eeb b\u1ec1 d\u00e0y l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c cho \u0111\u1ebfn danh ti\u1ebfng.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3i qua 26 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh El Geta \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 5 l\u1ea7n h\u1ea1 \u0111o v\u00e1n Real, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Getafe. C\u00f2n t\u1ea1i Bernabeu, ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng lu\u00f4n thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2008/09 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Getafe \u0111\u00e3 9 l\u1ea7n l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Los Blancos v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 9 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i ra v\u1ec1 trong cay \u0111\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Getafe, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. V\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7 khi m\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng s\u1ebd v\u1eabn thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c ch\u1edd Lopetegui<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Barca \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Alaves, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c CLB Real Madrid c\u0169ng s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 \u1edf cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Getafe v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i HLV Lopetegui \u0111ang g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng Real. Sau tr\u1eadn thua Atletico Madrid \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 51 tu\u1ed5i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i La Liga s\u1eafp t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u00edt \u1ecfi t\u1ea1i Real, vi\u1ec7c Lopetegui c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n La Liga s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, nh\u1ea5t khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Julen Lopetegui noi cung sau tran thua Atletico Madrid.\" title=\"HLV Julen Lopetegui n\u00f3i c\u1ee9ng sau tr\u1eadn thua Atletico Madrid.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Real-Madrid-guc-nga-truoc-Atletico-Khi-nhung-noi-nho-cu-day-them-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Julen Lopetegui \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i La Liga</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Getafe b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u0103m nay v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn sau khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 8 chung cu\u1ed9c. Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi Real, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Getafe kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 b\u1ecb suy gi\u1ea3m m\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh kh\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0&nbsp; David Soria, Vitorino Antunes, Ignasi Miquel v\u00e0 Nemanja Maksimovic.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng \u00edt c\u00e1c C\u0110V Real c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y lo ng\u1ea1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1ed1 1 Cristiano Ronaldo sau m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n l\u00fac n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Los Blancos v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng sau tr\u1eadn thua Atletico Madrid \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau cup ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Real \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u sai l\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1edfi l\u00fd do \u0111\u00f3, Real \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Getafe d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t &lsquo;con m\u1ed3i ngon&rsquo; c\u1ee7a Los Blancos trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn Real Madrid h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Getafe v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p nh\u01b0ng khi m\u00e0 Los Blancos \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb h\u00f3a l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Lopetegui \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 La Liga s\u1ebd v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid: \u00c1lvaro Odriozola, Jes\u00fas Vallejo (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng).<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Getafe: Markel Bergara (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng); Djen\u00e9 Dakonam (kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid (4-3-3): Navas; Ramos, Varane, Carvajal, Marcelo; Casemiro, Isco, Kroos; Bale, Asensio, Benzema.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Getafe (4-4-2): Soria; Gonzalez, Dakoman, Suarez, Antunes; Maksimovic, Portillo, Ndiaye; Molina, Rodriguez.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n&nbsp;Real Madrid vs Getafe: 2-1.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/3-ly-do-khien-real-madrid-tro-thanh-cuu-vuong-o-sieu-cup-chau-au-180-194621.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/3-ly-do-khien-real-madrid-tro-thanh-cuu-vuong-o-sieu-cup-chau-au.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/3-ly-do-khien-real-madrid-tro-thanh-cuu-vuong-o-sieu-cup-chau-au-180-194621.html\">3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Real Madrid tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf Si\u00eau cup ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn thua 4-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico Madrid c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a CLB Real Madrid trong su\u1ed1t 18 n\u0103m qua. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sep-real-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-modric-180-194607.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/sep-real-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-modric.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sep-real-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-modric-180-194607.html\">S\u1ebfp Real l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric</span><br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Emilio Butragueno c\u1ee7a Real kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Modric \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Bernabeu, qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t m\u1ecdi tin \u0111\u1ed3n xung quanh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018-184-194606.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018-184-194606.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018</span><br>\r\nSau bi\u1ebft bao n\u1ed7i \u0111au tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c, Atletico Madrid cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ee5c th\u00f9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Real Madrid v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/te-nhat-sau-60-nam-lich-su-real-madrid-hlv-julen-lopetegui-noi-cung-180-194577.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/Real-Madrid-guc-nga-truoc-Atletico-Khi-nhung-noi-nho-cu-day-them-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/te-nhat-sau-60-nam-lich-su-real-madrid-hlv-julen-lopetegui-noi-cung-180-194577.html\">T\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 60 n\u0103m l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Real Madrid, HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u1eabn n\u00f3i c\u1ee9ng</span><br>\r\nHLV Julen Lopetegui kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Atletico trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2519","checkdouble":"194788"},{"date":"08:42 19/08","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 19/8 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/19/lich-thi-dau-asiad-2018-ngay-hom-nay-198-cua-doan-ttvn.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h xin g\u1eedi t\u1edbi qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e1c m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao \u1edf ASIAD 2018 di\u1ec5n ra trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 19/8 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c V\u0110V thu\u1ed9c \u0111o\u00e0n Th\u1ec3 thao Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Chi\u1ec1u nay, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tranh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D v\u1edbi Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h. HLV Park Hang-seo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1ee1ng s\u1ee9c khi m\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t - nh\u00ec v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng do ch\u00fang ta ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nC\u0169ng trong bu\u1ed5i chi\u1ec1u, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung xu\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn l\u00fac 18h30, g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y duy\u00ean n\u1ee3 Th\u00e1i Lan. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta b\u1edfi \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p n\u1eef Nh\u1eadt\u00a0B\u1ea3n qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTrong ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a ASIAD 2018, \"g\u00e0 son\" D\u01b0\u01a1ng Th\u00fay Vi c\u0169ng xu\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u1edf chung ki\u1ebfm thu\u1eadt n\u1eef b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb 12h. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1eef v\u00f5 s\u0129 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed9i dung th\u01b0\u01a1ng thu\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 trao huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u1ede m\u00f4n b\u01a1i, Ho\u00e0ng Qu\u00fd Ph\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n Huy Ho\u00e0ng tham d\u1ef1 v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i 200 m t\u1ef1 do nam l\u00fac 9h. C\u00f9ng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m, L\u00ea Nguy\u1ec5n Paul thi \u1edf n\u1ed9i dung 100 m h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p nam.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTrong ng\u00e0y 19/8, m\u00f4n taekwondo thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i v\u00e0 v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft 2 n\u1ed9i dung quy\u1ec1n nam, n\u1eef. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, m\u1ecdi ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed5 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u JCC Plenary.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNgay trong ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 21 b\u1ed9 huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao \u1edf c\u00e1c m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ea5u ki\u1ebfm (2), b\u1eafn s\u00fang (2), b\u01a1i l\u1ed9i (7), taekwondo (4), \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eadt (5) v\u00e0 wushu (1).\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 198 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 198 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/Lich-thi-dau-Asiad-2018-ngay-hom-nay-198-cua-doan-TTVN-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 198 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 198 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/lich-thi-dau-asiad-1.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 198 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 198 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/lich-thi-dau-asiad-2-1.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y 19/8 c\u1ee7a TTVN</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2518","checkdouble":"194789"},{"date":"03:08 19/08","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn Tottenham 3-1 Fulham","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-tottenham-31-fulham.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n trong th\u00e1ng 8. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb kh\u00e1c sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">9 &ndash; Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 9 trong 10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Fulham t\u1ea1i Premier League, ch\u1ec9 thua \u0111\u00fang 1 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 3/2013.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n19 &ndash; Fulham \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi trong 19 l\u1ea7n l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi d\u00e0i nh\u1ea5t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh (t\u00ednh trong s\u1ed1 20 \u0111\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 n\u0103m nay).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n19 &ndash; Spurs \u0111ang c\u00f3 chu\u1ed7i 19 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n trong 10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn Tottenham 3-1 Fulham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn Tottenham 3-1 Fulham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/Nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-Tottenham-3-1-Fulham-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kane h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n th\u00e1ng 8, gi\u00fap Tottenham h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Fulham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n1065 - B\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Fulham l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Kane ghi b\u00e0n trong th\u00e1ng 8 sau 1065 ph\u00fat t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n4 &ndash; Sessegnon \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n ho\u1eb7c ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o trong 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Fulham tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng (1 b\u00e0n, 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n13 &ndash; K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Fulham v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 2, Mitrovic \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 13 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Mohamed Salah (14) l\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n h\u01a1n trong s\u1ed1 4 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n6 &ndash; Moura \u0111\u00e3 in d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 7 l\u1ea7n xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp Tottenham (2 b\u00e0n, 4 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n24 &ndash; Kane \u0111\u00e3 ghi 24 b\u00e0n sau 36 tr\u1eadn derby London cho Tottenham (trung b\u00ecnh 0.67 b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn). Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal l\u00e0 Thierry Henry c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 10 tr\u1eadn derby London tr\u1edf l\u00ean (43 b\u00e0n trong 59 tr\u1eadn &ndash; trung b\u00ecnh 0.73 b\u00e0n m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Tottenham vs Fulham:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-tottenham-vs-fulham-31-highlights-premier-league-2018-326-194766.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Tottenham 3-1 Fulham (V\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/harry-kane-noi-gi-sau-khi-hoa-giai-loi-nguyen-thang-8-172-194769.html\">Harry Kane n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n th\u00e1ng 8?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2517","checkdouble":"194770"},{"date":"03:19 19/08","title":"Hazard: \"Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra ma thu\u1eadt d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/hazard-chelsea-co-the-tao-ra-ma-thuat-duoi-thoi-sarri.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Hazard kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc ma thu\u1eadt d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea v\u1eeba v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Arsenal trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o ra m\u00e0n r\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 gay c\u1ea5n trong hi\u1ec7p 1. Chelsea v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Pedro v\u00e0 Morata. Nh\u01b0ng Arsenal c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng v\u1eeba khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 Iwobi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng sang hi\u1ec7p 2, Chelsea l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Marcos Alonso.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Hazard Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra ma thu\u1eadt d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Hazard Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra ma thu\u1eadt d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/hazard-chelsea-co-the-tao-ra-ma-thuat-duoi-thoi-sarri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Hazard t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c HLV Sarri sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHazard ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 60 m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n do ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. V\u00e0 anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 Alonso ki\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho The Blues.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb nh\u01b0ng Hazard t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Sarri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. V\u1eady n\u00ean d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 15 hay 20 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u0169ng lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Sarri l\u00e0 m\u1eabu HLV mu\u1ed1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i th\u00ec r\u1ea5t th\u00edch \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n m\u1ecdi l\u00fac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ma thu\u1eadt. V\u1eady n\u00ean th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t khi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t HLV nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede Premier League, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng. Sarri th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng HLV c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem video tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279447\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/19/chelsea-arsenal-1534617138.mp4&autoplay=false&mute=false&vtype=1&playType=0&_admParamTvc=0;0;0;0&_listsuggest=https://kenh14s.cnnd.vn/Handler/Video/ListVideoXML.ashx?watch=0&postroll=true&replay=true&nonVol=true&volume=0.6&boxVideoID=ifVideo-0&nopre=true&midroll=0.8;20s&urlParent=http://kenh14.vn/truc-tiep-h2-chelsea-3-2-arsenal-marcos-alonso-lap-cong-20180818161138825.chn\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2516","checkdouble":"194771"},{"date":"03:32 19/08","title":"T\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chievo, Ronaldo v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Allegri khen ng\u1ee3i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/tit-ngoi-truoc-chievo-ronaldo-van-duoc-hlv-allegri-khen-ngoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Alex Iwobi \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea v\u1eeba qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i theo c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City v\u00e0 Chelsea. \u1ede tr\u1eadn khai m\u00e0n Premier League, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City khi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p qu\u00e1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. H\u1ecd b\u1ecb Chelsea d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm 2 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. Ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a The Gunners \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi Marcos Alonso t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng cho Chelsea \u1edf ph\u00fat 81 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alex Iwobi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alex Iwobi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/iwobi-keu-goi-cac-dong-doi-dung-day-sau-that-bai-truoc-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Iwobi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Emery \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 17 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf sau khi v\u00f2ng 2 k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, sao tr\u1ebb Alex Iwobi \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 Arsenal v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn. Nh\u01b0ng anh c\u0169ng k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Arsenal x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1nh, \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi nhau v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, Arsenal s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn derby London n\u1eefa. L\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n West Ham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Video tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279447\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/19/chelsea-arsenal-1534617138.mp4&autoplay=false&mute=false&vtype=1&playType=0&_admParamTvc=0;0;0;0&_listsuggest=https://kenh14s.cnnd.vn/Handler/Video/ListVideoXML.ashx?watch=0&postroll=true&replay=true&nonVol=true&volume=0.6&boxVideoID=ifVideo-0&nopre=true&midroll=0.8;20s&urlParent=http://kenh14.vn/truc-tiep-h2-chelsea-3-2-arsenal-marcos-alonso-lap-cong-20180818161138825.chn\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/emery-hai-long-du-arsenal-thua-dang-chelsea-172-194773.html\">Emery h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 Arsenal thua \u0111au Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-chelsea-co-the-tao-ra-ma-thuat-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-194771.html\">Hazard: Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra ma thu\u1eadt d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2515","checkdouble":"194772"},{"date":"03:43 19/08","title":"Emery h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 Arsenal thua \u0111au Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/emery-hai-long-du-arsenal-thua-dang-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Emery kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y l\u1ea1c quan sau tr\u1eadn thua 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea \u0111\u00eam qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Premier League d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi t\u00e2n HLV Emery. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi nh\u00e1t dao ch\u00ed t\u1eed c\u1ee7a Marcos Alonso \u1edf ph\u00fat 81 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Emery kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y l\u1ea1c quan khi th\u1ea5y m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn thua Man City ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 Arsenal thua \u0111au Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Emery h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 Arsenal thua \u0111au Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/emery-hai-long-du-arsenal-thua-dang-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Emery h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 Arsenal thua \u0111au Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thua. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00f3 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu 3 b\u00e0n thua. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n. T\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 chung cu\u1ed9c l\u00e0 3-2 nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1c \u0111i n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, Chelsea th\u1eadt ra c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n h\u01a1n. C\u00e1ch ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng sau khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc ngay trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cHi\u1ec7p hai l\u00e0 l\u00fac ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u00e1p s\u00e1t hay ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n trao cho h\u1ecd nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u00f2n Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 l\u00e0 3-2. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi \u0111i nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ecf. Trong hi\u1ec7p hai, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi hai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 19 v\u00e0 21 tu\u1ed5i. H\u1ecd \u0111ang d\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac d\u00f9 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 chung cu\u1ed9c kh\u00f4ng cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 n\u00e0o\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-chelsea-vs-arsenal-32-highlights-premier-league-2018-326-194768.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal (V\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-chelsea-co-the-tao-ra-ma-thuat-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-194771.html\">Hazard: Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra ma thu\u1eadt d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2514","checkdouble":"194773"},{"date":"03:56 19/08","title":"Pochettino n\u1ed5i kh\u00f9ng sau khi b\u1ecb h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Alderweireld","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/pochettino-noi-khung-sau-khi-bi-hoi-ve-tuong-lai-alderweireld.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Mauricio Pochettino \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed5i gi\u1eadn th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi b\u1ecb c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Alderweireld.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alderweireld \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Fulham sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 h\u1eadu World Cup 2018. Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Man United tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Alderweireld v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Spurs.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1eabn c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Alderweireld ra \u0111i v\u1eabn tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7y c\u00e1c m\u1eb7t b\u00e1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pochettino n\u1ed5i kh\u00f9ng sau khi b\u1ecb h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Alderweireld h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pochettino n\u1ed5i kh\u00f9ng sau khi b\u1ecb h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Alderweireld h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/pochettino-noi-khung-sau-khi-bi-hoi-ve-tuong-lai-alderweireld.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pochettino n\u1ed5i kh\u00f9ng sau khi b\u1ecb h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Alderweireld</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Fulham, HLV Pochettino \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Alderweireld. V\u00e0 v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed5i kh\u00f9ng v\u00e0 n\u00f3i li\u00ean h\u1ed3i trong v\u00f2ng 5 ph\u00fat. Sau \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u00fd ch\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f3m t\u1eaft l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb b\u00e0i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Pochettino.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ri\u00eang t\u01b0. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n, v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i, d\u00f9 h\u1ecd l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai. Khi \u0111\u00f3, li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Levy v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn hay kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ed1c to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. Kh\u00f4ng ai n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i c\u1ea3. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n c\u1edfi m\u1edf v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. N\u1ebfu h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n v\u1ec1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e2u\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Tottenham:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-tottenham-vs-fulham-31-highlights-premier-league-2018-326-194766.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Tottenham 3-1 Fulham (V\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/harry-kane-noi-gi-sau-khi-hoa-giai-loi-nguyen-thang-8-172-194769.html\">Harry Kane n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n th\u00e1ng 8?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2513","checkdouble":"194774"},{"date":"04:06 19/08","title":"Iwobi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/iwobi-keu-goi-cac-dong-doi-dung-day-sau-that-bai-truoc-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Alex Iwobi \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea v\u1eeba qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i theo c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City v\u00e0 Chelsea. \u1ede tr\u1eadn khai m\u00e0n Premier League, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City khi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p qu\u00e1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. H\u1ecd b\u1ecb Chelsea d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm 2 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. Ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a The Gunners \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi Marcos Alonso t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng cho Chelsea \u1edf ph\u00fat 81 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alex Iwobi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alex Iwobi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/iwobi-keu-goi-cac-dong-doi-dung-day-sau-that-bai-truoc-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Iwobi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Emery \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 17 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf sau khi v\u00f2ng 2 k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, sao tr\u1ebb Alex Iwobi \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 Arsenal v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn. Nh\u01b0ng anh c\u0169ng k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Arsenal x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1nh, \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi nhau v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, Arsenal s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn derby London n\u1eefa. L\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n West Ham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Video tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279447\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/19/chelsea-arsenal-1534617138.mp4&autoplay=false&mute=false&vtype=1&playType=0&_admParamTvc=0;0;0;0&_listsuggest=https://kenh14s.cnnd.vn/Handler/Video/ListVideoXML.ashx?watch=0&postroll=true&replay=true&nonVol=true&volume=0.6&boxVideoID=ifVideo-0&nopre=true&midroll=0.8;20s&urlParent=http://kenh14.vn/truc-tiep-h2-chelsea-3-2-arsenal-marcos-alonso-lap-cong-20180818161138825.chn\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/emery-hai-long-du-arsenal-thua-dang-chelsea-172-194773.html\">Emery h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 Arsenal thua \u0111au Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-chelsea-co-the-tao-ra-ma-thuat-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-194771.html\">Hazard: Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra ma thu\u1eadt d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2512","checkdouble":"194775"},{"date":"04:20 19/08","title":"Thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n, Arsenal c\u1ee7a Emery t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 26 n\u0103m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/thua-2-tran-lien-arsenal-cua-emery-te-nhat-sau-26-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsenal d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Emery \u0111ang c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Premier League trong v\u00f2ng 26 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Arsenal thay th\u1ebf HLV Wenger t\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua. Sau 22 n\u0103m n\u1eb1m d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Wenger, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Arsenal c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n m\u00ecnh sang m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00e0ng l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 HLV Emery. Arsenal kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Man City. Ti\u1ebfp ngay sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n t\u1edbi hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ecba Stamford Bridge c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 l\u00e0 Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n, Arsenal c\u1ee7a Emery t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 26 n\u0103m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n, Arsenal c\u1ee7a Emery t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 26 n\u0103m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/thua-2-tran-lien-arsenal-cua-emery-te-nhat-sau-26-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n, Arsenal c\u1ee7a Emery t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 26 n\u0103m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u1edbi Arsenal trong v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n. V\u00e0 nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Arsenal sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-2 mu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c h\u01a1n khi Arsenal l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi hai b\u00e0n tay tr\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng khi b\u1ecb Chelsea d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-0. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 Iwobi. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Marcos Alonso \u1edf ph\u00fat 81 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n cho The Blues.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 2 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Premier League sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n. <strong>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a 1992/93</strong>. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3, Arsenal m\u1edf m\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn thua 2-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Norwich tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb Blackburn \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGeorge Graham l\u00e0 HLV d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 1992/93 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 10.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>HLV Emery c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 thua c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi Steve Burtenshaw.</strong> Khi n\u1eafm gi\u1eef vai tr\u00f2 HLV t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n, Burtenshaw \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 3 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n th\u00e1ng 3 \u2013 th\u00e1ng 4 n\u0103m 1986.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2511","checkdouble":"194776"}]}